{"id":"architecture_decision","prompt":"Evaluate whether a privacy-first local assistant should use a system-level mixture of experts. Give a clear recommendation, three concrete risks, and a minimal MVP plan.","category":"reasoning","complexity":"complex","task_checks":[{"id":"substantive","type":"min_words","value":80},{"id":"required_coverage","type":"contains_all_groups","groups":[["recommend","decision"],["risk"],["mvp","minimum viable"]]}],"quality_rubric":[{"id":"decision_coverage","description":"States an explicit recommendation or decision.","type":"contains_any","values":["recommend","decision","should"],"weight":0.3},{"id":"risk_coverage","description":"Discusses risks.","type":"contains_any","values":["risk","failure","limitation","trade-off","tradeoff"],"weight":0.3},{"id":"mvp_coverage","description":"Defines an MVP or minimum viable scope.","type":"contains_any","values":["mvp","minimum viable","first iteration"],"weight":0.3},{"id":"bounded_length","description":"Avoids an excessively long answer.","type":"max_words","value":500,"weight":0.1}]}
{"id":"context_strategy","prompt":"Compare sliding window, summary memory, and semantic retrieval for a local assistant. Select a hybrid strategy and explain the main trade-offs.","category":"reasoning","complexity":"complex","task_checks":[{"id":"substantive","type":"min_words","value":70},{"id":"covers_options","type":"contains_all_groups","groups":[["sliding window","window"],["summary memory","summary"],["semantic retrieval","retrieval"],["hybrid"]]}],"quality_rubric":[{"id":"comparison","description":"Covers all three named approaches.","type":"contains_all_groups","groups":[["window"],["summary"],["retrieval"]],"weight":0.45},{"id":"selection","description":"Selects a hybrid strategy.","type":"contains_any","values":["hybrid","combine","combination"],"weight":0.3},{"id":"tradeoffs","description":"Explains trade-offs.","type":"contains_any","values":["trade-off","tradeoff","trade off","cost","latency"],"weight":0.25}]}
{"id":"incident_plan","prompt":"A local model endpoint becomes intermittently unavailable during user requests. Diagnose likely causes and propose a phased mitigation plan including observability and fallback behavior.","category":"operations","complexity":"very_complex","task_checks":[{"id":"substantive","type":"min_words","value":90},{"id":"required_coverage","type":"contains_all_groups","groups":[["cause","diagnos"],["observability","metric","log"],["fallback","retry","circuit breaker"],["phase","step"]]}],"quality_rubric":[{"id":"diagnosis","description":"Identifies likely causes.","type":"contains_any","values":["cause","timeout","memory","process","network"],"weight":0.3},{"id":"observability","description":"Includes observable diagnostics.","type":"contains_any","values":["observability","metric","log","trace","health"],"weight":0.25},{"id":"fallback","description":"Defines fallback behavior.","type":"contains_any","values":["fallback","retry","circuit breaker"],"weight":0.25},{"id":"phasing","description":"Uses a phased or ordered plan.","type":"contains_any","values":["phase","first","step 1","immediate"],"weight":0.2}]}
{"id":"privacy_flow","prompt":"Design a tool-using flow for a local assistant that reads private documents, remembers user preferences, and answers without sending sensitive content to the cloud. Include trust boundaries and auditability.","category":"privacy","complexity":"very_complex","task_checks":[{"id":"substantive","type":"min_words","value":90},{"id":"required_coverage","type":"contains_all_groups","groups":[["document"],["memory","preference"],["trust boundary","trust boundaries"],["audit"]]}],"quality_rubric":[{"id":"document_flow","description":"Describes document processing.","type":"contains_any","values":["document","ingest","retrieve"],"weight":0.2},{"id":"memory","description":"Addresses preference memory.","type":"contains_any","values":["memory","preference"],"weight":0.2},{"id":"privacy","description":"Keeps sensitive data local.","type":"contains_all_groups","groups":[["local","device"],["sensitive","private","privacy"]],"weight":0.25},{"id":"trust","description":"Defines trust boundaries.","type":"contains_any","values":["trust boundary","trust boundaries","boundary"],"weight":0.2},{"id":"audit","description":"Includes auditability.","type":"contains_any","values":["audit","log","trace"],"weight":0.15}]}
{"id":"concise_rewrite","prompt":"Rewrite this in a clear, warm, concise tone using at most 55 words: 'I am not convinced this architecture is the right one. It may be making the project unnecessarily difficult, but I would like us to investigate whether it has genuine product value before we discard it.'","category":"writing","complexity":"simple","task_checks":[{"id":"nonempty","type":"nonempty"},{"id":"word_limit","type":"max_words","value":55}],"quality_rubric":[{"id":"concise","description":"Respects the requested word limit.","type":"max_words","value":55,"weight":0.45},{"id":"preserves_uncertainty","description":"Preserves the uncertainty in the source.","type":"contains_any","values":["not convinced","unsure","uncertain","not sure"],"weight":0.25},{"id":"preserves_value_question","description":"Preserves the request to examine product value.","type":"contains_all_groups","groups":[["investigat","explore","assess"],["value","viable","potential"]],"weight":0.3}]}
{"id":"three_bullet_summary","prompt":"Summarize the following in exactly three bullet points: The prototype routes tasks between a strong general model and a faster fallback. It stores local memory, exposes health diagnostics, and can call tools manually. Current evidence measures routing accuracy, but it does not yet prove better answer quality than a single model.","category":"summary","complexity":"simple","task_checks":[{"id":"three_bullets","type":"matches_regex","pattern":"(?m)^(?:[-*] .+\\n){2}[-*] .+$"},{"id":"concise","type":"max_words","value":90}],"quality_rubric":[{"id":"routing","description":"Mentions routing or the two model roles.","type":"contains_any","values":["rout","general model","fallback"],"weight":0.25},{"id":"capabilities","description":"Covers memory and operational capabilities.","type":"contains_all_groups","groups":[["memory"],["health","diagnostic"],["tool"]],"weight":0.35},{"id":"evidence_limit","description":"Preserves a negative quality-evidence limitation through explicit negation, evidence strength, answer quality, and the single-model baseline.","type":"matches_regex","pattern":"(?s)\\b(?:does not(?: yet)?|has not(?: yet)?|no)\\b.{0,120}\\b(?:prov\\w*|demonstrat\\w*|improv\\w*)\\b.{0,120}\\b(?:answer )?quality\\b.{0,120}\\b(?:single model|one model)\\b","weight":0.4}]}
{"id":"italian_product_plan","prompt":"In italiano, proponi un piano in quattro passi per validare un orchestratore MoE locale. Includi baseline, qualità, latenza e un criterio go/no-go.","category":"planning","complexity":"medium","task_checks":[{"id":"italian_terms","type":"contains_all_groups","groups":[["baseline"],["qualità","qualita"],["latenza"],["go/no-go","go no-go"]]},{"id":"substantive","type":"min_words","value":60}],"quality_rubric":[{"id":"baseline","description":"Defines a baseline.","type":"contains_any","values":["baseline","modello singolo"],"weight":0.25},{"id":"quality","description":"Defines a quality measure.","type":"contains_any","values":["qualità","qualita","rubrica"],"weight":0.25},{"id":"latency","description":"Defines a latency measure.","type":"contains_any","values":["latenza","tempo di risposta"],"weight":0.25},{"id":"decision","description":"Defines a go/no-go criterion.","type":"contains_any","values":["go/no-go","go no-go","soglia"],"weight":0.25}]}
{"id":"security_review","prompt":"Review a local web UI bound to 0.0.0.0 with no authentication. Explain the threat, recommend an immediate safe default, and list two follow-up controls.","category":"security","complexity":"medium","task_checks":[{"id":"substantive","type":"min_words","value":60},{"id":"required_coverage","type":"contains_all_groups","groups":[["threat","risk","expos"],["127.0.0.1","localhost","loopback"],["auth"],["control","follow-up","follow up"]]}],"quality_rubric":[{"id":"threat","description":"Explains network exposure.","type":"contains_any","values":["expos","network","remote","unauthorized"],"weight":0.3},{"id":"safe_default","description":"Recommends loopback binding.","type":"contains_any","values":["127.0.0.1","localhost","loopback"],"weight":0.3},{"id":"authentication","description":"Recommends authentication or authorization.","type":"contains_any","values":["authentication","authorization","auth"],"weight":0.2},{"id":"transport_or_firewall","description":"Adds another defense-in-depth control.","type":"contains_any","values":["tls","firewall","reverse proxy","rate limit"],"weight":0.2}]}
